        "name": "Cruelty",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "The harm you deal with your corrupting touch saps the strength from your enemy's body. You can cast *touch of the void* targeting a living creature using 2 actions instead of 1. If you do, the target is also enfeebled 1 for 1 minute if it fails its save (enfeebled 2 if it critically fails).",
